subSubSection.paragraph:
Antheromorpha harpaga
- 
Jeekel 1980
: 85 (M); 
Golovatch 1983
: 181 (M); 
Enghoff et al. 2004
: 37 (M); 
Nguyen and Sierwald 2013
: 1234 (M).

This is the only species in this genus that has been reported from Vietnam (
Attems 1937
). It differs from congeners in the gonopod solenophore being deeply bifid and showing a long and slender process d and a bidentate tip (Fig. 20C).
